28
00:01:33,699 --> 00:01:35,420
Sir, they've shown themselves.

29
00:01:38,820 --> 00:01:41,579
Good. Take them alive.

30
00:02:07,037 --> 00:02:09,207
Official Gu!

31
00:02:22,825 --> 00:02:26,432
ظآزEven if I drift
within a darkened whirlظآز

32
00:02:26,712 --> 00:02:30,761
ظآزKindred souls
meet the light and become oneظآز

33
00:02:30,762 --> 00:02:38,574
ظآزSo many chapters,
every wound rememberedظآز

34
00:02:38,575 --> 00:02:42,299
ظآزBack where we once stood,
the blossoms still remainظآز

35
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:45,932
ظآزThe night runs deep like watching eyesظآز

36
